$ nvm current - show the current version the terminal is using

$ nvm ls - list of nodes versions in your computer

$ nvm ls-remote - list the nodes versions avaliable to download

$ nvm install node - install the most recent version of node

$ nvm install vX.X.X - install the specified version

$ nvm uninstall vX.X.X - unistall the specified version

$ nvm use node - use the most recent version of node

$ nvm use vX.X.X - use the specified version

$ nvm alias default vX.X.X - define a default version

* defining a specific version for a project

  - Create a file and naming: ".nvmrc"
  - In the file, type the version 



